        <div style="flex: 2; max-width: 60%; position: relative;">
            <h2 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left;">
                Chameleons in danger!
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.18em; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; text-align: left; color: #ebefe8;">
                Nearly <strong style="color: #ff8d8d; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em;">38%</strong> of chameleons are at risk of extinction. The destruction of their forests and global warming are making their survival increasingly difficult.<br>
                Protecting nature also means saving these incredible lizards.
            </p>
            <a id="UICNLink" href="https://icun.org" target="_blank" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; width: 100%; right: 0;">
                <p style="text-align: left; color: #dedede;">International Union for Conservation of Nature (UICN)</p>
            </a>
